      <title>世界银行表示泰国利率适当、中性</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/world-bank-says-thai-interest-rates-appropriate-neutral-2024-03-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[世界银行周三在曼谷举行的一次活动中表示，泰国的利率水平适合当前形势，并且是中性的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/world-bank-says-thai-interest-rates-appropriate-neutral-2024-03-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 05:06:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瓦努阿图警方在美国海岸警卫队的协助下称中国船只违反了捕鱼法</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/vanuatu-police-aided-by-us-coast-guard-say-chinese-vessels-violated-fishing-laws-2024-03-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瓦努阿图警方和官员表示，当地警方检查了六艘中国渔船，这些渔船是第一艘在瓦努阿图海域巡逻的美国海岸警卫队船只，其中六艘中国渔船违反了瓦努阿图的渔业法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/vanuatu-police-aided-by-us-coast-guard-say-chinese-vessels-violated-fishing-laws-2024-03-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 04:58:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国警方就实习医生罢工问题向医疗机构官员询问</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-police-question-medical-body-officials-over-trainee-doctors-walkout-2024-03-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三，韩国警方因指控医生协会违反医疗法而对他们进行询问，当局不断向见习医生施压，要求他们结束为期两周的罢工并返回医院。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-police-question-medical-body-officials-over-trainee-doctors-walkout-2024-03-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 04:34:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾央行行长排除“很快”放松利率的可能性</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/philippine-central-bank-governor-rules-out-easing-rates-soon-2024-03-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于通胀风险上升，菲律宾央行行长周三排除了短期内降息的可能性，并暗示借贷成本将在更长时间内保持较高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/philippine-central-bank-governor-rules-out-easing-rates-soon-2024-03-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 04:28:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>越南与澳大利亚签署能源矿产合作谅解备忘录</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/vietnam-australia-sign-mou-energy-mineral-cooperation-2024-03-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[越南工业和贸易部周三表示，越南总理范明正正在访问墨尔本期间，越南和澳大利亚将签署能源和矿产合作谅解备忘录。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/vietnam-australia-sign-mou-energy-mineral-cooperation-2024-03-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 03:52:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>报道称马来西亚预计澳大利亚公司投资50亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/malaysia-expecting-australian-firms-invest-5-bln-reports-say-2024-03-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据国家通讯社马新社周三援引总理安瓦尔·易卜拉欣的话报道，马来西亚预计澳大利亚公司将在该国投资高达 245 亿林吉特（51.7 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/malaysia-expecting-australian-firms-invest-5-bln-reports-say-2024-03-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 03:35:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国股市引领亚洲走低，金价创历史新高后震荡</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-03-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚洲股市周三在谨慎交易中走软，其中中国股市下滑，因为北京方面缺乏大规模刺激措施令一些投资者感到失望，而黄金和比特币在触及历史新高后有所回落。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-03-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 02:37:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚航空公司因解雇提出 COVID-19 安全问题的员工而被罚款</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/australias-qantas-fined-firing-worker-who-raised-covid-19-safety-concerns-2024-03-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚澳洲航空 (Qantas Airways) 因非法解雇一名员工而被罚款 250,000 澳元（162,375 美元），该员工在 COVID-19 大流行初期告诉员工不要清洁从中国抵达的飞机，这加剧了该航空公司的声誉挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/australias-qantas-fined-firing-worker-who-raised-covid-19-safety-concerns-2024-03-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 01:46:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新加坡星展银行 2023 年可持续融资额增长 37%，达到 521 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/sustainable-finance-reporting/singaporean-bank-dbs-grows-sustainable-financing-by-37-521-bln-2023-2024-03-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新加坡最大的银行星展集团周三表示，截至 12 月底，扣除还款后的可持续融资承诺从 2022 年的 510 亿新元增加了 37.3%，达到 700 亿新元（合 521 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/sustainable-finance-reporting/singaporean-bank-dbs-grows-sustainable-financing-by-37-521-bln-2023-2024-03-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 00:45:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚经济放缓，凸显降息的理由</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-economy-grows-meagre-02-q4-spending-sputters-2024-03-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于家庭收入的严重挤压导致消费者支出陷入停滞，澳大利亚经济在去年第四季度以蜗牛般的速度增长，强化了市场对下一步利率下调的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-economy-grows-meagre-02-q4-spending-sputters-2024-03-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 00:40:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
